# Contact form delivery (free, no backend) — Web3Forms.
# 1. Go to https://web3forms.com and enter the email where you want enquiries.
# 2. They email you an access key. Paste it below.
# 3. Copy this file to `.env.local`, fill the value, and restart `npm run dev`.
#    On your host (e.g. Vercel), add the same variable in the project settings.
NEXT_PUBLIC_WEB3FORMS_KEY=your-web3forms-access-key-here
